 SQLU HA/DR Week – Database Mirroring Performance Counters 
 SQL U - HA/DR Week 
Database mirroring debuted in SQL Server 2005 and had eleven performance counters for monitoring mirroring. There were ten new performance counters released with SQL Server 2008. We now have twenty-one performance counters to use for monitoring database mirroring. A list with a brief description of each can be found i